    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kiosk Simulator is an action-packed comedic take on the hustles of running a big city kiosk and the nostalgia of reaching that lone open kiosk on a rainy late night.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Demo Disclaimer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > This demo is a showcase of only the core gameplay features. This includes everyday Kiosk business (ordering, restocking, selling, cleaning), and the fighting system. More gameplay mechanics will be added and tested in this demo over time. Also, please consider that technical problems will arise, especially with the addition of the online multiplayer feature. If you encounter bugs, reporting them to us helps a lot!<br><br>Many Thanks and we hope you enjoy our game!<br><br><strong>Neptun Interactive</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113700/extras/cabd2c4a98930a5b7ad861c10ee549e2.poster.avif?t=1753433957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113700/extras/cabd2c4a98930a5b7ad861c10ee549e2.webm?t=1753433957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113700/extras/cabd2c4a98930a5b7ad861c10ee549e2.mp4?t=1753433957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Roleplay</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the role of a kiosk’s owner in Cologne, Germany. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Restock, serve customers, maintain and protect your kiosk against robbery and vandalism! </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multiplayer</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run the shop together with a friend in Split screen Co-op Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or Online with friends</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Vibrant Cast and Dynamic Gameplay</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each customer could be a loyal customer, a potential shoplifter or even a troublemaker! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113700/extras/d90b6dde75e477761a65e83880603d18.poster.avif?t=1753433957\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113700/extras/d90b6dde75e477761a65e83880603d18.webm?t=1753433957\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113700/extras/d90b6dde75e477761a65e83880603d18.mp4?t=1753433957\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Progression</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Restock the Kiosk with better products</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade to new furniture and better security</p></li></ul>",
